{
  "enabled": true,
  "name": "SDID Flow Test",
  "description": "一鍵跑 SDID Task-Pipe 整合測試，自動建測試專案、跑完整流程、產出改善建議報告",
  "version": "1",
  "when": {
    "type": "userTriggered"
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "請執行 SDID Flow Tester skill。\n\n讀取 .agent/skills/sdid-flow-tester/SKILL.md，然後執行：\nnode .agent/skills/sdid-flow-tester/scripts/run-flow-test.cjs --flow=taskpipe --type=todo\n\n腳本跑完後，讀取 stdout 中 ═══ 區塊之間的報告內容，用 SKILL.md 定義的報告格式整理後回覆使用者。"
  }
}